ge-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android-iOS/dp/B0CCT2LWT8?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Backbone One Gen 2 (USB-C)</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android-iOS/dp/B0CCT2LWT8?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android-iOS\/dp\/B0CCT2LWT8?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Android-iOS/dp/B0CCT2LWT8?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">$70 (was $100)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>This is the "Gen 2" version of the controller that has a reshaped D-pad and magnetic adapters that allow you to fit it to your phone without needing to remove the protective cover if it's standard-sized. These are designed to connect directly to an iPhone or Android smartphone, giving you an experience that transforms your device into your very own handheld gaming console. All the inputs you'd expect from a modern controller--analogue sticks, face and shoulder buttons, triggers, and more--are here and housed inside a compact frame. When not in use, the Backbone One can be folded up to reduce its size.</p><p>The USB-C version is available in black at this price, but it looks like the model that sports a PS5-inspired white finish is currently out of stock.</p></div>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Lightning-iOS/dp/B0CT17GPNT?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Lightning-iOS\/dp\/B0CT17GPNT?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Lightning-iOS/dp/B0CT17GPNT?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Backbone One Gen 1 (Lightning)</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Lightning-iOS/dp/B0CT17GPNT?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Lightning-iOS\/dp\/B0CT17GPNT?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/BACKBONE-Mobile-Gaming-Controller-Lightning-iOS/dp/B0CT17GPNT?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">$60 (was $100)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>The Lightning version of the Backbone One is designed for iPhone 14 and older smartphones. This deal is also for the Gen 1 model, which will require you to remove your protective cover from your iPhone to use it. Only the white version of the controller cradle is currently available for this deal. </p>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console\/dp\/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Backbone Pro</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console\/dp\/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/Backbone-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Pro-Level-Console/dp/B0DQM23MLZ?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">$170</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>For more controller options, you can also check out the Backbone Pro. This is the premium edition of the smartphone controller, as it's equipped with redesigned ergonomics and high-quality components like a textured finish, quieter face buttons, full-sized ALPS analog sticks, Hall Effect triggers, and two remappable back buttons. This model is pricier, but if you'd like a premium cradle for your smartphone, you can get this for $170. </p>                      </div>   </div><p>The other big deal we've spotted is for 8BitDo's own Android smartphone controller. Normally $50, it's currently on sale for $22 for the black version, and $34 for the white version. It's compatible with a wide array of Android devices that can fit inside its 100mm to 170mm base, and you're getting some top-quality components here. This cradle has Hall Effect joysticks and triggers, back paddle buttons, a turbo function, and wear-resistant metal joystick rings. Since it's compatible with 8BitDo Ultimate Software V2, you can also customize it extensively.</p><figure data-align="center" data-size="large" data-img-src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4581501-8bitdoultimate.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4581501" data-ratio="0.5625" data-width="1280" data-embed-type="image"><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4581501-8bitdoultimate.jpg" data-ref-id="1300-4581501"></a><figcaption>8bitDo Ultimate Mobile Controller</figcaption><img src="https://www.gamespot.com/a/uploads/original/1601/16018044/4581501-8bitdoultimate.jpg"></figure><ul><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Ultimate-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Joysticks-Console/dp/B0DK36N98Q?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">8Bitdo Ultimate Mobile Gaming Controller (Black)</a> -- $22 (<del>$50</del>)</li><li><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Ultimate-Gaming-Controller-Bluetooth-Joysticks-Console/dp/B0DK37CSHP?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">8Bitdo Ultimate Mobile Gaming Controller (White</a>) -- $34 (<del>$50</del>)</li></ul><p>If you use a tablet to play games, you can also save a few bucks on Razer's new line of Kishi controllers. The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Kishi-Gaming-Controller-Android-Tablets-Smartphone/dp/B0DVKWZ5SX?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Kishi V3 Pro XL</a> is for users who run with larger tablets, as it can fit 11- and 13-inch iPad Pro and Air models inside its frame, and it has several high-end components in its construction.</p><p>This has large ergonomic handles, anti-drift TMR thumbsticks that Razer claims are superior to Hall Effect thumbsticks, and extremely responsive actuation in the triggers and face buttons. Normally $200, it's on sale for $170.</p><p>For more Prime Big Deal Days discounts, check out <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/amazon-prime-day-deals/">GameSpot's deals hub</a> as we continue to update it with the latest specials.</p><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>           